## Build output
bin/
obj/
publish/

## User-specific / machine-specific files (never share these)
*.user
*.suo

## Rider / JetBrains project settings
.idea/
*.DotSettings.user

# Exception: keep the spell-checker dictionary if you add custom words
# later (the old console project did this too - it's just a word list,
# genuinely useful to share so Rider doesn't flag your own terms as
# typos on a clean clone).
!.idea/dictionaries/
!.idea/dictionaries/*.xml

## OS clutter
Thumbs.db
.DS_Store

## Twitch / secrets (nothing here yet, but never let these slip in)
.env
*.env
secrets.json
appsettings.*.json
!appsettings.json
*.token